  --[[ Mechanic  variants ]]--


*Default
**Woodie mode
 -Sanity boost from planting stuff
 -Log meter visible and drops
 -Log meter drops faster when chopping
 -Log meter increses when eating woodstuffs
 -Transforms at 25 beaverness
 -Beareded
 -The whole "politeness" thing

**Beaver mode
 -Log meter still drops
 -Log meter increses when eating woodstuffs or gnawing things
 -Health & sanity
 -25% damage absorption
 -pathetic 27.2 damage
 -sanity drains at a rate of 1.5/min
 -weather affects him
 -keeps inventory
 -starves at 0 beaverness

